{
  "html": "<p>Install our Python SDK using <a href=\"https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/\"><code>pip</code></a>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ pip <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --upgrade sentry-sdk<span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token number\">0.16</span>.2</code></pre></div>\n<p>Import and initialize the Sentry SDK early in your application's setup:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python highlight\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> sentry_sdk\nsentry_sdk<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>init<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"___PUBLIC_DSN___\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>One way to verify your setup is by intentionally sending an event that breaks your application.</p>\n<p>Raise an unhandled Python exception by inserting a divide by zero expression\ninto your application:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py highlight\"><code class=\"language-py\">division_by_zero <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span></code></pre></div>", 
  "link": "https://docs.sentry.io/error-reporting/quickstart/?platform=python", 
  "id": "python", 
  "name": "Python"
}
